### 3.6 Tags Table

```sql
-- ============================================
-- TAGS TABLE
-- Purpose: Content tags/hashtags for discovery
-- Priority: P0
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE tags (
  id          UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  name        VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  slug        VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
  usage_count INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
  is_nsfw     BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
  is_banned   BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
  is_pending  BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
  banned_reason VARCHAR(255),
  created_at  TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW(),
  updated_at  TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);

CREATE INDEX idx_tags_slug ON tags(slug);
CREATE INDEX idx_tags_usage_count ON tags(usage_count DESC);

-- For tag suggestions (active, non-banned tags)
CREATE INDEX idx_tags_active ON tags(slug, usage_count DESC) 
  WHERE is_banned = FALSE AND is_pending = FALSE;

-- For moderation queue
CREATE INDEX idx_tags_pending ON tags(created_at DESC) 
  WHERE is_pending = TRUE;
```

**Design Notes:**
- `slug` is URL-safe version of tag name (lowercase, no spaces)
- `usage_count` denormalized for trending tags feature
- `is_pending` for new tags awaiting moderation
- `is_banned` for prohibited tags

