## 9. Migration Strategy

### 9.1 Implementation Order

> **APPROVED APPROACH:** All tables created in single initial migration to avoid future migration complexity.

**Single Migration — All Tables (Dependency Order):**

| Order | Table | Dependencies |
|-------|-------|--------------|
| 1 | `admin_roles` | None |
| 2 | `admin_permissions` | `admin_roles` |
| 3 | `user_admin_roles` | `admin_roles`, `users` |
| 4 | `tags` | None |
| 5 | `post_tags` | `tags`, `posts` |
| 6 | `comments` | `posts`, `users` |
| 7 | `comment_likes` | `comments`, `users` |
| 8 | `tip_goals` | `creator_profiles` |
| 9 | `tip_goal_contributions` | `tip_goals`, `transactions` |
| 10 | `subscription_history` | `subscriptions` |
| 11 | `user_activity` | None (partitioned) |
| 12 | `bundles` | `creator_profiles` |
