| 14 | `bundle_purchases` | `bundles`, `transactions` |

**Partitioning — Applied at Creation:**

| Table | Notes |
|-------|-------|
| `user_activity` | Born partitioned |
| `notifications` | Create as partitioned from start |
| `transactions` | Create as partitioned from start |
| `messages` | Create as partitioned from start |
