| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|
| Partition migration complexity | Medium | High | Start with new tables; convert existing gradually |
| High-volume table performance | Medium | High | Partition `user_activity` from day one |
| Foreign key limitations on partitions | Certain | Medium | Document; enforce at application level |
| Index bloat on high-write tables | Medium | Medium | Regular REINDEX; monitor |
| Admin permission complexity | Low | Low | Start with predefined roles only |

